extendedInfo.description: Put your friend's head on a punching dummy!  Or, choose from the faces included in-game to punch jerks you love to hate.This "re-inflation" of the classic punching dummy will give you hours of bruise-inducing fun.  Earn coins in game to buy faces and bodies.  Punch with Boxing Gloves, Knife Gloves, or Monster Hands.This app is ad-supported.  A paid, in-game option exists to remove ads.Keywords: Punch, Dummy, Face, Head, Blood, Bash, Boss, Politician, Politics, Republican, Democrat, Rich
